<div class="mainhistoryfaq">
<a>How do I get my durable purchase original invoice copy?
</a>
<p>We would like to inform you that the original invoice copies and loan documents are maintained with us for our records. You may contact the dealer should you wish to retrieve a copy of the same.<br />
<br />
